14
00:01:57,189 --> 00:01:59,924
左上, 左下.
Yah! Left high, left low.

15
00:02:02,629 --> 00:02:05,463
<i>( Swords clanging )</i>

16
00:02:17,510 --> 00:02:19,579
右下, 右刺.
Right low, lunge right.

17
00:02:22,748 --> 00:02:25,449
你要是弄坏什么东西, 修女会要了我的命.
You break anything, the Septa will have my head.

18
00:02:25,484 --> 00:02:27,284
怎么...
- What is-- - ( Screaming )

19
00:02:38,361 --> 00:02:41,129
你妹妹很清楚我们今天要走.
Your sister knew perfectly well we were to leave today.

20
00:02:41,163 --> 00:02:43,331
- 她怎么会忘记... - 她没有忘记.
- How she could forget-- - She didn't forget.

21
00:02:43,365 --> 00:02:46,067
她跟她的舞蹈老师在一起. 每天早上都是.
She's with her dancing master. She's with him every morning.

22
00:02:46,102 --> 00:02:48,638
她总是带着满身瘀伤回来. 她真是笨手笨脚.
She always comes back with scrapes and bruises. She's so clumsy.

23
00:02:48,671 --> 00:02:50,573
<i>别出声!
- ( Swords clanging ) - Hush!</i>

24
00:02:50,608 --> 00:02:52,808
回你的房间去.
Go back to your room.

25
00:02:53,743 --> 00:02:55,146
插上门闩
Bar the doors

26
00:02:55,180 --> 00:02:57,381
绝不要给不认识的人开门.
and do not open them for anyone you do not know.

27
00:02:57,415 --> 00:03:00,084
- 怎么了? 出什么事了? - 照我说的做.
- What is it? What's happening? - Do as I told you.

28
00:03:00,118 --> 00:03:01,919
快跑!
Run!

29
00:03:05,657 --> 00:03:07,324
<i>这边!
Man: This way!</i>

30
00:03:07,359 --> 00:03:10,828
<i>( Reaming )</i>

31
00:03:20,836 --> 00:03:23,004
左, 右. 右!
Left, right. Rah!

32
00:03:23,038 --> 00:03:24,740
现在你死了.
Now you are dead.

33
00:03:24,774 --> 00:03:26,741
你说的是右边,
You said right,

34
00:03:26,776 --> 00:03:28,644
但你打的却是左边.
but you went left.

35
00:03:28,677 --> 00:03:30,878
结果你是个死女孩了.
And now you are a dead girl.

36
00:03:30,913 --> 00:03:32,514
可是你骗人了.
Only 'cause you lied.

37
00:03:32,549 --> 00:03:35,182
我的舌头骗人了. 可我的眼睛...
My tongue lied. My eyes

38
00:03:35,216 --> 00:03:38,420
说的是真话. 只是你没看见.
shouted the truth. You were not seeing.

39
00:03:38,454 --> 00:03:40,956
我明明看了, 但你...
I was so. I watched, but you--

40
00:03:40,990 --> 00:03:44,460
看了不等于看见了, 死女孩.
watching is not seeing, dead girl.

41
00:03:46,530 --> 00:03:50,165
只有看见, 只有真正的洞察,
The seeing, the true seeing,

42
00:03:50,199 --> 00:03:52,635
才是剑术的精髓.
that is the heart of swordplay.

43
00:03:52,670 --> 00:03:54,805
<i>( Door opens )</i>

44
00:03:57,141 --> 00:03:59,644
艾莉亚史塔克, 跟我们走.
Arya Stark, come with us.

45
00:03:59,677 --> 00:04:02,413
你父亲要见你.
Your father wants to see you.

46
00:04:02,448 --> 00:04:04,816
可是为什么...
And why is it

47
00:04:04,849 --> 00:04:07,284
艾德大人会派兰尼斯特家的人...
that Lord Eddard is sending Lannister men

48
00:04:07,318 --> 00:04:09,521
而不是他自己的手下来呢? 我很好奇.
in place of his own? I am wondering.

49
00:04:09,555 --> 00:04:12,623
别不识好歹, 舞蹈老师.
Mind your place, dancing master.

50
00:04:12,657 --> 00:04:15,193
<i>此事与你无关.
This is no concern of yours.</i>

51
00:04:15,227 --> 00:04:17,062
我父亲才不会派你们来呢.
My father wouldn't send you.

52
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:23,300
而且我也不想跟你们走.
And I don't have to go with you if I don't want.

53
00:04:23,334 --> 00:04:25,670
抓住她.
( Laughs ) Take her.

54
00:04:25,704 --> 00:04:29,673
你们是人还是蛇, 居然威胁一个小孩子?
Are you men or snakes, that you would threaten a child?

55
00:04:29,707 --> 00:04:31,843
给我滚开, 矮家伙.
Get out of my way, little man.

56
00:04:31,877 --> 00:04:35,346
<i>我是西利欧佛瑞尔...
I am Syrio Forel...</i>

57
00:04:35,379 --> 00:04:37,380
外国杂种.
Foreign bastard.

58
00:04:40,117 --> 00:04:43,821
...你跟我讲话要放尊重点.
...And you will be speaking to me with more respect.

59
00:04:43,855 --> 00:04:46,456
宰了这布拉佛斯人, 把那女孩抓来.
Kill the Braavosi. Bring the girl.

60
00:04:47,994 --> 00:04:50,728
小艾莉亚, 今天我们的舞蹈课至此为止.
Arya child, we are done with dancing for the day.

61
00:04:50,762 --> 00:04:53,398
跑去找你父亲吧.
Run to your father.

62
00:05:13,887 --> 00:05:16,622
该死的东西.
- Bloody oafs. - ( Sword rings )

63
00:05:16,656 --> 00:05:18,524
快走, 艾莉亚.
Be gone now, Arya.

64
00:05:18,559 --> 00:05:21,127
跟我一起走. 快跑.
Come with me. Run.

65
00:05:22,764 --> 00:05:25,766
布拉佛斯的首席剑士从不临阵脱逃.
The first sword of Braavos does not run.

66
00:05:37,911 --> 00:05:39,812
<i>记不记得我们应该
( Wood clatters )</i>

67
00:05:37,911 --> 00:05:39,812
What do we say

68
00:05:39,848 --> 00:05:41,781
怎么对死神说话?
to the God of death?

69
00:05:41,816 --> 00:05:43,683
"今天不行."
Not today.

70
00:05:45,218 --> 00:05:46,653
快走.
Go.

71
00:05:49,656 --> 00:05:52,191
( Lannister men moaning )

72
00:05:55,961 --> 00:05:59,463
<i>- ( Swords ringing ) - ( Men screaming )</i>

73
00:06:12,211 --> 00:06:14,312
今天不行. 今天不行.
Not today. Not today.

74
00:06:17,617 --> 00:06:19,718
( Gasps )

75
00:06:23,856 --> 00:06:25,658
你不要过来.
Stay away from me.

76
00:06:25,692 --> 00:06:27,358
我要告诉我父亲.
I'll tell my father.

77
00:06:27,394 --> 00:06:30,362
我要... 我要告诉王后.
I'll-- I'll tell the Queen.

78
00:06:30,396 --> 00:06:34,098
你以为是谁派我来的?
( Chuckles ) Who do you think sent me?

79
00:06:37,937 --> 00:06:40,406
<i>( Horses neigh )</i>

80
00:06:46,612 --> 00:06:48,480
缝衣针.
Needle.

81
00:06:51,718 --> 00:06:53,752
原来她在这儿.
There she is.

82
00:06:53,786 --> 00:06:56,053
- 你想要什么? - 我要抓你, 小狼女.
- What do you want? - I want you, wolf girl.

83
00:06:56,088 --> 00:06:57,790
- 过来. - 不要过来.
- Come here. - Leave me be.

84
00:06:57,824 --> 00:06:59,891
我父亲是首相. 他会奖赏你的.
My father's a lord. He'll reward you.

85
00:06:59,925 --> 00:07:01,492
<i>会奖赏我的是王后!
She'll reward me-- the Queen!</i>

86
00:07:01,526 --> 00:07:03,694
走开!
- Stay away! - ( Gasps )

87
00:07:14,507 --> 00:07:17,108
<i>( Door clanging, creaking )</i>

88
00:07:32,793 --> 00:07:36,428
史塔克大人, 你一定渴了.
Lord Stark, you must be thirsty.

89
00:07:37,865 --> 00:07:40,033
瓦里斯.
Varys.

90
00:07:41,836 --> 00:07:44,137
我向你保证里面没有下毒.
I promise you it isn't poisoned.

91
00:07:45,807 --> 00:07:48,108
为什么没人肯信任太监呢?
Why is it no one ever trusts the eunuch?

92
00:07:56,651 --> 00:07:58,420
不太多, 大人.
Not so much, My Lord.

93
00:07:58,454 --> 00:08:00,488
如果我是你的话, 我会留下一点.
I would save the rest, if I were you.

94
00:08:00,523 --> 00:08:04,392
藏好它. 在这地牢里常有人被渴死.
Hide it. Men have been known to die of thirst in these cells.

95
00:08:06,262 --> 00:08:08,764
我的女儿们怎么样了?
What about my daughters?

96
00:08:08,798 --> 00:08:11,334
小的那个看来已经逃出了红堡.
The younger one seems to have escaped the castle.

97
00:08:11,369 --> 00:08:13,569
连我的小小鸟们都找不到她.
Even my little birds cannot find her.

98
00:08:13,603 --> 00:08:17,139
- 珊莎呢? - 依然是乔佛里的未婚妻.
- And Sansa? - Still engaged to Joffrey.

99
00:08:17,173 --> 00:08:20,744
瑟曦会把她留在身边. 但你家其他的人...
Cersei will keep her close. The rest of your household though--

100
00:08:20,778 --> 00:08:22,946
全死了, 我感到很痛心.
all dead, it grieves me to say.

101
00:08:22,980 --> 00:08:25,247
我讨厌看到流血.
I do so hate the sight of blood.

102
00:08:26,750 --> 00:08:29,619
我的手下被屠杀时你却袖手旁观.
You watched my men being slaughtered and did nothing.

103
00:08:29,653 --> 00:08:31,955
我只能那样, 大人.
And would again, My Lord.

104
00:08:31,989 --> 00:08:36,392
我既没武器, 又没盔甲, 还被兰尼斯特的武士团团围住.
I was unarmed, unarmored and surrounded by Lannister swords.

105
00:08:36,427 --> 00:08:38,760
你看我象个大英雄吗?
When you look at me do you see a hero?

106
00:08:44,701 --> 00:08:47,068
究竟是什么疯狂念头让你去告诉王后...
What madness led you to tell the Queen

107
00:08:47,104 --> 00:08:49,905
说你知道乔佛里的真实身世?
you had learned the truth about Joffrey's birth?

108
00:08:52,275 --> 00:08:54,243
仁慈的疯狂念头.
The madness of mercy.

109
00:08:55,946 --> 00:08:58,681
希望她能保住她孩子们的性命.
That she might save her children.

110
00:08:58,716 --> 00:09:00,548
<i>啊, 孩子们.
Ah, the children.</i>

111
00:09:00,583 --> 00:09:03,452
受苦的总是那些无辜者.
It is always the innocents who suffer.

112
00:09:03,486 --> 00:09:06,388
杀死国王的不是那袋酒, 也不是那只野猪.
It wasn't the wine that killed Robert, nor the boar.

113
00:09:06,423 --> 00:09:09,892
酒令他反应迟缓, 野猪撕开了他的肚子,
The wine slowed him down and the boar ripped him open,

114
00:09:09,926 --> 00:09:13,160
但是真正杀死国王的却是你的仁慈.
but it was your mercy that killed the King.

115
00:09:16,731 --> 00:09:20,100
我想你知道自己在劫难逃吧, 艾德大人?
I trust you know you are a dead man, Lord Eddard?

116
00:09:24,838 --> 00:09:27,407
王后不会杀我.
The Queen can't kill me.

117
00:09:27,442 --> 00:09:29,909
凯特还抓着她的弟弟.
Cat holds her brother.

118
00:09:29,945 --> 00:09:32,645
可惜不是她爱的那个弟弟.
The wrong brother sadly.

119
00:09:32,681 --> 00:09:34,414
而且这会儿也跑了.
And lost to her.

120
00:09:34,448 --> 00:09:37,384
你夫人让小恶魔从她的指缝里钻了出去.
Your wife has let the Imp slip through her fingers.

121
00:09:41,222 --> 00:09:43,658
倘若真是这样,
If that's true,

122
00:09:43,692 --> 00:09:47,227
那快快割了我的喉咙, 做个了结.
then slit my throat and be done with it.

123
00:09:47,261 --> 00:09:49,831
今天不会, 大人.
Not today, My Lord.

124
00:09:52,869 --> 00:09:55,703
告诉我, 瓦里斯.
Tell me something, Varys.

125
00:09:55,739 --> 00:09:58,240
你究竟是为谁服务?
Who do you truly serve?

126
00:09:59,476 --> 00:10:02,144
为了国家, 大人.
The Realm, My Lord.

127
00:10:02,179 --> 00:10:04,447
总得有人为国家服务.
Someone must.

128
00:10:12,722 --> 00:10:14,557
<i>( Door creaks, clangs )</i>

129
00:10:23,432 --> 00:10:26,168
这是奥瑟, 肯定没错.
It's Othor, without a doubt.

130
00:10:27,504 --> 00:10:29,104
另外那个是杰佛佛花, 大人,
The other one is Jafer Flowers, My Lord,

131
00:10:29,139 --> 00:10:31,907
<i>他的一只手被狼咬掉了.
less the hand the wolf tore off.</i>

132
00:10:31,942 --> 00:10:34,943
有班扬或他手下其他人的踪迹吗?
Any sign of Benjen or the rest of his party?

133
00:10:34,979 --> 00:10:37,846
只有这两个, 大人.
Just these two, My Lord.

134
00:10:37,881 --> 00:10:39,883
我看他们死了有一阵子了.
Been dead awhile, I'd say.

135
00:10:39,918 --> 00:10:42,653
- 嗯. - 可是气味...
- Mmm. - The smell.

136
00:10:44,523 --> 00:10:46,024
( Sniffs )

137
00:10:46,058 --> 00:10:47,658
怎么气味?
What smell?

138
00:10:47,692 --> 00:10:50,729
没有气味.
There is none.

139
00:10:50,763 --> 00:10:54,499
如果他们死了很久, 怎么还没腐烂?
If they'd be dead for a long time, wouldn't there be rot?

140
00:10:54,533 --> 00:10:57,235
我们烧了他们吧.
We should burn them.

141
00:10:57,269 --> 00:11:00,304
雪诺说得没错, 大人. 烧掉尸体吧.
Snow's not wrong, My Lord. Fire will do for them.

142
00:11:00,339 --> 00:11:02,506
野人的处理方式.
The Wildling way.

143
00:11:02,542 --> 00:11:05,277
我要先让伊蒙师傅检查一下这些尸体.
I want Maester Aemon to examine them first.

144
00:11:05,311 --> 00:11:08,480
你也许是个懦夫, 塔利,
You may be a coward, Tarly,

145
00:11:08,514 --> 00:11:10,649
<i>但人倒是不笨.
but you're not stupid.</i>

146
00:11:10,682 --> 00:11:14,719
- 把他们弄进去. - 照他说的做.
- Get them inside. - You heard him.

147
00:11:16,254 --> 00:11:18,222
总司令,
Lord Commander,

148
00:11:18,256 --> 00:11:20,759
伊蒙师傅正在等你过去...
Maester Aemon awaits you in his chambers--

149
00:11:20,793 --> 00:11:24,629
君临城来了一只渡鸦.
a raven from King's Landing.

150
00:11:24,663 --> 00:11:26,530
快移出去.
Come on, move 'em out.

151
00:11:38,241 --> 00:11:41,109
给我倒杯酒, 雪诺,
Bring me a horn of ale, Snow,

152
00:11:41,144 --> 00:11:44,078
<i>再给你自己也倒一杯.
and pour one for yourself.</i>

153
00:11:53,889 --> 00:11:56,457
国王死了.
The King is dead.

154
00:12:08,570 --> 00:12:11,104
我父亲有什么消息?
Is there any word of my father?

155
00:12:11,138 --> 00:12:13,373
坐下.
Sit.

156
00:12:17,878 --> 00:12:20,412
史塔克大人...
Lord Stark has been

157
00:12:20,446 --> 00:12:23,048
被控叛国.
charged with treason.

158
00:12:23,081 --> 00:12:25,484
他们说他与劳勃的弟弟共谋
They say he conspired with Robert's brothers

159
00:12:25,518 --> 00:12:28,254
阻止乔佛里王子继位.
to deny the throne to Prince Joffrey.

160
00:12:40,602 --> 00:12:44,240
<i>我希望你别打算做任何傻事.
I hope you're not thinking of doing anything stupid.</i>

161
00:12:44,274 --> 00:12:47,710
如今你的职责所在是这里.
Your duty lies here now.

162
00:12:47,744 --> 00:12:50,812
我的妹妹也在君临.
My sisters were in King's Landing too.

163
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:55,250
我相信她们定会...
I'm sure they'll be

164
00:12:55,284 --> 00:12:57,086
受到妥善照顾.
treated gently.

165
00:13:00,222 --> 00:13:03,359
你的父亲犯下了严重的叛国罪.
Your father has proved to be an awful traitor, dear.

166
00:13:03,393 --> 00:13:06,863
劳勃国王尸骨未寒
King Robert's body was still warm

167
00:13:06,897 --> 00:13:11,167
艾德大人就密谋夺取乔佛里的王位.
when Lord Eddard began plotting to steal Joffrey's rightful throne.

168
00:13:11,201 --> 00:13:13,570
他绝不会做这种事.
He wouldn't do that.

169
00:13:13,605 --> 00:13:16,472
他知道我有多爱乔佛里. 他绝不会.
He knows how much I love Joffrey. He wouldn't.

170
00:13:16,508 --> 00:13:19,610
求求您, 王后陛下, 这一定是误会.
Please, Your Grace, there's been a mistake.

171
00:13:19,644 --> 00:13:23,280
找我父亲过来. 他会向您解释... 他是国王的朋友.
Send for my father. He'll tell you-- the King was his friend.

172
00:13:23,315 --> 00:13:26,384
亲爱的珊莎, 你是完全无辜的. 我们都明白.
Sansa sweetling, you are innocent of any wrong. We know that.

173
00:13:26,418 --> 00:13:29,919
<i>但你毕竟是个叛国者的女儿.
Yet you are the daughter of a traitor.</i>

174
00:13:29,953 --> 00:13:32,121
我怎么敢让你嫁给我儿子呢?
How can I allow you to marry my son?

175
