( Snarling, screaming )

350
00:26:22,369 --> 00:26:25,038
( Grunts )

351
00:26:26,240 --> 00:26:28,208
<i>( Screaming, snarling continue )</i>

352
00:26:32,046 --> 00:26:34,513
他们在干什么?
What did they do?

353
00:26:35,548 --> 00:26:36,811
<i>(羊人最适合当奴隶.)
( Rakharo speaking Dothraki )</i>

354
00:26:36,848 --> 00:26:40,352
(卓戈卡奥会把他们送给奴隶贩子.)

355
00:26:40,848 --> 00:26:43,352
(奴隶贩子会送给我们金钱.)

356
00:26:45,848 --> 00:26:49,352
(还有丝绸和钢铁.)

357
00:26:50,599 --> 00:26:53,969
我以为多斯拉克人不信赖金钱.
Daenerys: I thought the Dothraki didn't believe in money.

358
00:26:54,002 --> 00:26:57,905
金钱可以雇船, 公主,
Gold to hire ships, Princess,

359
00:26:57,940 --> 00:27:00,776
乘船才能去维斯特洛.
ships to sail to Westeros.

360
00:27:03,747 --> 00:27:06,781
<i>( Louder screaming )</i>

361
00:27:16,558 --> 00:27:19,027
乔拉, 叫他们住手.
Jorah, make them stop.

362
00:27:19,060 --> 00:27:21,295
- 卡丽熙? - 你听到我的命令了.
- Khaleesi? - You heard me.

363
00:27:21,329 --> 00:27:24,832
这些人为卡奥流血卖命, 如今该他们取得奖赏了.
These men have shed blood for their Khal. Now they claim their rewards.

364
00:27:24,865 --> 00:27:26,968
(她是个羊女, 卡丽煕.)
( Rakharo speaking )

365
00:27:27,066 --> 00:27:28,968
(我们的战士上她是看得起她.)

366
00:27:29,066 --> 00:27:30,968
(要是她的哭嚎冒犯了卡丽煕.)

367
00:27:31,066 --> 00:27:33,968
(我去把她的舌头割了.)

368
00:27:35,679 --> 00:27:38,047
公主, 你的心肠很软,
Princess, you have a gentle heart,

369
00:27:38,080 --> 00:27:40,083
<i>但战争就是这个样子.
but this is how it's always been.</i>

370
00:27:40,116 --> 00:27:43,086
我的心肠并不软, 爵士.
I do not have a gentle heart, Ser.

371
00:27:43,116 --> 00:27:46,086
(照我的命令办, 否则卡奥惟你是问)

372
00:27:51,628 --> 00:27:53,895
<i>(住手!)
( Rakharo speaks )</i>

373
00:27:55,499 --> 00:27:58,000
<i>(吾血之血. 她是我的!)
Kash qoy qoyi thira disse. Me qorasokh anni!</i>

374
00:27:58,034 --> 00:28:02,170
<i>- 来吧. - (她是我抓到的!)
- Come. - Man: Anha afichak mae m'arakhoon!</i>

375
00:28:02,203 --> 00:28:05,873
(你小心一点.)
( Speaks Dothraki )

376
00:28:07,409 --> 00:28:09,277
你要怎么处置她?
What do you want done with them?

377
00:28:09,311 --> 00:28:11,878
把她带到我这儿来. 还有那些女人.
Bring her to me. And those women there.

378
00:28:13,749 --> 00:28:16,182
您没法把她们全都收为己有, 公主.
You cannot claim them all, Princess.

379
00:28:16,217 --> 00:28:18,251
我能,
I can,

380
00:28:18,286 --> 00:28:20,988
我就要这样做.
and I will.

381
00:28:21,022 --> 00:28:22,990
(操!)
Man: Me Fati!

382
00:28:23,023 --> 00:28:26,493
(卡丽熙抢了我的战利品,)
Khaleesi vazha anhaan qorasokh anni,

383
00:28:26,528 --> 00:28:28,863
(本该是让我骑的羊女!)
ch'anha afichak mae m'arakhoon anni!

384
00:28:28,896 --> 00:28:31,732
(等我见到她,)
Drogo: Me vastoe hatif anni;

385
00:28:31,767 --> 00:28:34,469
<i>(我会问一下这件事.)
ahhazaan yer Nemo vacchaki.</i>

386
00:28:35,396 --> 00:28:38,132
(我生命中的月亮,)

387
00:28:38,396 --> 00:28:42,132
(马戈说你抢了他的战利品.)

388
00:28:42,396 --> 00:28:46,132
(一个本该让他骑的羊人之女.)

389
00:28:46,396 --> 00:28:49,132
(告诉我是怎么回事.)

390
00:28:50,396 --> 00:28:55,132
(马戈说的是实话, 我的日和星.)

391
00:28:55,896 --> 00:28:58,132
(今天我是收了许多羊女...)

392
00:28:58,297 --> 00:29:00,132
(不让她们被人骑...)

393
00:29:03,797 --> 00:29:05,132
(战争就是这样.)

394
00:29:05,797 --> 00:29:08,132
(现在这些女人是奴隶...)

395
00:29:08,297 --> 00:29:11,132
(...随我们高兴摆布.)

396
00:29:12,297 --> 00:29:14,132
(那我高兴让她们平安.)

397
00:29:15,297 --> 00:29:18,132
(若你的战士要骑她们, 就要将她们收作妻子.)

398
00:29:20,297 --> 00:29:22,731
(马会和羊交配吗?)

399
00:29:23,797 --> 00:29:26,132
(马和羊都是龙的食物!)

400
00:29:27,797 --> 00:29:29,832
(你是个外族人.)

401
00:29:30,297 --> 00:29:32,132
(你无权命令我.)

402
00:29:32,297 --> 00:29:35,132
(我是卡丽熙, 我有权命令你.)

403
00:29:35,396 --> 00:29:38,132
( Drogo snickers )

404
00:29:37,797 --> 00:29:40,132
(看她变得多凶猛?)

405
00:29:40,797 --> 00:29:44,132
(这是因为她怀着我的儿子, 骑着世界的骏马,)

406
00:29:45,396 --> 00:29:47,132
(让她充满火焰.)

407
00:29:48,396 --> 00:29:50,132
(我听明白了.)

408
00:29:51,396 --> 00:29:53,132
(马戈, 找别地方去发泄吧.)

409
00:29:53,848 --> 00:29:55,249
( Spits )

410
00:29:55,797 --> 00:29:59,132
(听从外族女人的卡奥还算是什么卡奥.)

411
00:30:00,521 --> 00:30:03,423
<i>(奥霍斯.)
( Drogo grunts ) Ohos.</i>

412
00:30:04,726 --> 00:30:06,593
<i>(让开.)
Os.</i>

413
00:30:11,826 --> 00:30:15,593
(我不会用火烧掉你的尸体.)

414
00:30:16,826 --> 00:30:19,593
(我不会给你那样的荣耀.)

415
00:30:24,826 --> 00:30:27,292
(我会让甲虫吃你的眼珠.)

416
00:30:27,326 --> 00:30:29,692
(我会让蛆虫爬满你的肺.)

417
00:30:35,326 --> 00:30:39,093
(我会让雨水落在你腐烂的皮肤上...)

418
00:30:40,326 --> 00:30:44,093
(...直到你只剩下一把骨头.)

419
00:30:48,326 --> 00:30:50,093
(你要先杀得死我才行.)

420
00:30:50,700 --> 00:30:51,800
(你就要死了.)
( Gasps )

421
00:31:11,700 --> 00:31:12,800
(我的日和星受伤了.)

422
00:31:14,900 --> 00:31:15,701
(只是破了点皮...)

423
00:31:15,900 --> 00:31:16,701
(...我生命中的月亮.)

424
00:31:17,900 --> 00:31:19,701
(医者在哪儿?)

425
00:31:20,900 --> 00:31:22,701
(让飞虫咬了一口而已.)

426
00:31:23,000 --> 00:31:25,933
<i>(我可以帮伟大的骑马战士疗伤.)
( Woman speaking Dothraki )</i>

427
00:31:24,567 --> 00:31:26,634
( Gasps )

428
00:31:26,768 --> 00:31:29,634
(卡奥不需要跟羊交配的女人帮忙.)

429
00:31:31,768 --> 00:31:33,035
(她是我的人, 让她说.)

430
00:31:34,210 --> 00:31:36,345
谢谢您, 银发夫人.
Thank you, silver lady.

431
00:31:38,582 --> 00:31:41,048
你是谁?
Who are you?

432
00:31:41,084 --> 00:31:44,019
我叫弥丽马兹笃尔. 是这座神庙的女祭司.
I am named Mirri Maz Duur. I was the Godswife of this Temple.

433
00:31:44,052 --> 00:31:45,653
(巫魔女.)
( Spits )

434
00:31:45,688 --> 00:31:48,423
我母亲是从前的女祭司.
My mother was Godswife here before me.

435
00:31:48,458 --> 00:31:50,893
她教会我如何调制圣烟和圣膏.
She taught me how to make healing smokes and ointments.

436
00:31:50,926 --> 00:31:53,930
<i>所有人类都是同一群羔羊, 这是我们的信仰.
All men are of one flock, so my people believe.</i>

437
00:31:53,964 --> 00:31:56,066
至高牧神派我到世上医治他的...
The Great Shepherd sent me to Earth to heal his--

438
00:31:56,365 --> 00:32:00,066
(巫魔女太多话了. 会毒害耳朵.)

439
00:32:01,707 --> 00:32:03,708
不论是羔羊或是狮子,
lamb or lion,

440
00:32:03,741 --> 00:32:06,411
他的伤口必须立刻清洗缝针
his wound must be washed and sewn

441
00:32:06,444 --> 00:32:08,711
<i>不然会化脓的.
or it will fester.</i>

442
00:32:09,845 --> 00:32:11,711
(让她给你清洗伤口吧, 我的日和星...)

443
00:32:12,045 --> 00:32:14,112
(看见你流血让我心痛.)

444
00:32:33,502 --> 00:32:35,703
<i>( Men chatting, eating )</i>

445
00:32:37,307 --> 00:32:40,609
三十年来我杀死过...
For 30 years I've been making corpses

446
00:32:40,644 --> 00:32:42,478
无数敌人, 小子.
out of men, boy.

447
00:32:42,512 --> 00:32:45,247
我最适合率领前锋.
I'm the man you want leading the Vanguard.

448
00:32:46,615 --> 00:32:48,782
盖伯特葛洛佛才该率领前锋.
Galbart Glover will lead the Van.

449
00:32:48,817 --> 00:32:51,484
除非他妈的长城整个融化
The bloody Wall will melt

450
00:32:51,519 --> 00:32:54,587
否则安伯家别想走在葛洛佛家前头.
before an Umber marches behind a Glover.

451
00:32:55,423 --> 00:32:57,657
<i>我要率领前锋
I will lead the Van</i>

452
00:32:57,692 --> 00:32:59,992
否则我就带着我的人马
or I will take my men

453
00:33:00,027 --> 00:33:02,127
班师回家.
and march them home.

454
00:33:07,067 --> 00:33:09,736
欢迎你这么做, 安伯大人.
You are welcome to do so, Lord Umber.

455
00:33:09,770 --> 00:33:12,839
等我收拾完兰尼斯特家
And when I am done with the Lannisters

456
00:33:12,874 --> 00:33:15,174
我会立刻回师北上,
I will march back North,

457
00:33:15,210 --> 00:33:16,676
把你从你的城堡里抓出来
root you out of your Keep

458
00:33:16,711 --> 00:33:19,381
并当成背誓者吊死.
and hang you for an oathbreaker.

459
00:33:19,414 --> 00:33:21,415
背誓者, 是吗?!
Oathbreaker, is it?!

460
00:33:22,984 --> 00:33:25,554
我可不会干坐着任人侮辱
I'll not sit here and swallow insults

461
00:33:25,587 --> 00:33:28,123
特别是象你这种刚从泥里钻出来的小鬼, 八成连尿都还有青草气.
from a boy so green he pisses grass.

462
00:33:29,157 --> 00:33:30,959
( Snarls )

463
00:33:30,992 --> 00:33:33,694
<i>( Screaming )</i>

464
00:33:42,304 --> 00:33:44,605
我父亲曾教导我必须以死刑惩戒...
My Lord father taught me it was death to bare steel

465
00:33:44,638 --> 00:33:46,707
<i>敢对主君拔剑的封臣.
- against your Liege Lord. - ( Huffs )</i>

466
00:33:46,740 --> 00:33:51,045
但我相信大琼恩只是想帮我切肉罢了.
But doubtless the Greatjon only meant to cut my meat for me.

467
00:33:53,082 --> 00:33:55,517
你的肉...
Your meat...

468
00:34:00,656 --> 00:34:03,326
还真他妈的硬.
is bloody tough.

469
00:34:04,228 --> 00:34:06,395
<i>( Chortles )</i>

470
00:34:08,099 --> 00:34:10,467
( All laughing )

471
00:34:33,960 --> 00:34:36,929
- 怎么了? 出什么事了? - 嘘, 没什么.
- What is it? What's happened? - Shh, it's all right.

472
00:34:41,402 --> 00:34:44,971
- 你要去哪儿? - 去南方. 去救父亲.
- Where are you going? - South. For father.

473
00:34:45,005 --> 00:34:46,706
可现在是午夜啊.
But it's the middle of the night.

474
00:34:46,740 --> 00:34:48,875
兰尼斯特家的探子无处不在.
The Lannisters have spies everywhere.

475
00:34:48,909 --> 00:34:51,476
我不希望让他们知道我们已经出发.
I don't want them to know we're coming.

476
00:34:51,512 --> 00:34:54,213
他们的人马比我们多.
They have more men than we do.

477
00:34:54,248 --> 00:34:56,449
嗯, 是这样的.
Aye, they do.

478
00:34:56,483 --> 00:34:58,550
我能和你一起去吗?
Can't I come with you?

479
00:34:58,585 --> 00:35:01,086
现在我能骑马了. 你看过我骑马了.
I can ride now. You've seen me riding.

480
00:35:01,121 --> 00:35:03,222
我不会再惹麻烦的, 我...
And I won't get in the way, I--

481
00:35:03,257 --> 00:35:05,791
临冬城必须有史塔克家的人坐镇.
There must always be a Stark at Winterfell.

482
00:35:05,826 --> 00:35:07,960
在我回来之前你就是城主.
Until I return that will be you.

483
00:35:10,431 --> 00:35:13,699
我们走后你绝不能离开城堡. 明白吗?
You are not to leave the castle walls while we are gone. Do you understand?

484
00:35:16,338 --> 00:35:19,706
好好听从鲁温师傅的教导. 好好照顾你的弟弟.
Listen to Maester Luwin. Look after your little brother.

485
00:35:19,742 --> 00:35:21,876
我会的.
I will.

486
00:35:21,911 --> 00:35:23,978
我有时间就会写信回来,
I'll send letters whenever I can,

487
00:35:24,012 --> 00:35:26,248
但如果你很久没收到我的信,
but if you don't hear from me,

488
00:35:26,282 --> 00:35:28,184
也不要担心.
don't be scared.

489
00:35:33,291 --> 00:35:35,492
我会回来的.
Until I return.

490
00:35:55,715 --> 00:35:58,782
你躲在那儿多久了?
How long have you been hiding out there?

491
00:35:58,818 --> 00:36:02,286
罗柏会找你道别.
Robb will be looking for you to say goodbye.

492
00:36:03,623 --> 00:36:05,556
他们全都走了.
They've all gone away.

493
00:36:05,592 --> 00:36:08,527
他们很快就会回来. 罗柏会救出父亲
They'll be back soon. Robb will free father

494
00:36:08,561 --> 00:36:10,762
他们会和母亲一道回来.
and they'll come back with mother.

495
00:36:12,431 --> 00:36:14,934
不, 他们不会.
No, they won't.

496
00:36:19,606 --> 00:36:21,708
<i>请你们务必看顾罗柏.
Bran: Please watch over Robb.</i>

497
00:36:21,742 --> 00:36:24,210
也请你们看顾临冬城所所有人马.
And watch over all the other men from Winterfell.

498
00:36:24,244 --> 00:36:27,413
还有, 还有席恩.
And Theon too, I suppose.

499
00:36:33,119 --> 00:36:35,887
你听见了吗, 孩子?
You hear them, boy?

500
00:36:35,922 --> 00:36:38,523
旧神正在回答你.
The Old Gods are answering you.

501
00:36:38,557 --> 00:36:40,458
你在这里做什么?
What are you doing here?

502
00:36:40,492 --> 00:36:43,362
他们也是我的神.
They're my Gods too.

503
00:36:44,864 --> 00:36:48,467
在长城之外, 他们是惟一的真神.
Beyond the Wall, they're the only Gods.

504
00:36:49,836 --> 00:36:52,139
即便奴隶也可以祈祷.
Even slaves are allowed to pray.

505
00:36:52,172 --> 00:36:54,541
你可不是奴隶.
You're not a slave.

506
00:36:56,610 --> 00:36:59,579
嗯, 你的朋友确实曾经拿刀抵住我的喉咙.
Well, your friend did put a knife to my throat.

507
00:37:00,715 --> 00:37:03,317
我不是在抱怨, 小领主,
I'm not complaining, Little Lord,

508
00:37:03,351 --> 00:37:06,085
只是说出事实.
just telling truths.

509
00:37:07,387 --> 00:37:10,190
你说听见神说话是什么意思?
What did you mean about hearing the Gods?

510
00:37:10,224 --> 00:37:12,559
你向他们祈求,
You asked them,

511
00:37:12,592 --> 00:37:14,226
而他们正在回答.
they're answering you.

512
00:37:14,262 --> 00:37:17,231
嘘.
Shh.

513
00:37:17,264 --> 00:37:18,931
竖起耳朵.
Open your ears.

514
00:37:18,965 --> 00:37:21,367
<i>( Leaves rustling )</i>

515
00:37:24,371 --> 00:37:26,606
不过是风声.
It's only the wind.

516
00:37:26,641 --> 00:37:29,643
你以为这风是谁送来的?
Who do you think sends the wind

517
00:37:29,677 --> 00:37:31,644
如果不是诸神的话?
if not the Gods?

518
00:37:31,679 --> 00:37:33,380
他们能看到你, 孩子.
They see you, boy.

519
00:37:33,414 --> 00:37:35,817
<i>他们也能听到你说话.
They hear you.</i>

520
00:37:35,851 --> 00:37:37,418
<i>( Sighs )</i>

521
00:37:37,452 --> 00:37:40,289
在你哥哥要去的地方, 他们无法帮他.
Your brother will get no help from them where he's going.

522
00:37:40,322 --> 00:37:43,125
旧神在南方没有力量.
The Old Gods have no power in the South.

523
00:37:43,159 --> 00:37:46,829
那儿的鱼梁木早已被砍伐一空.
The Weirwoods there were all cut down a long time ago.

524
00:37:46,864 --> 00:37:49,632
没有眼睛, 他们如何看顾你哥哥呢?
How can they watch when they have no eyes?

525
00:37:49,666 --> 00:37:51,067
<i>( Running footsteps )</i>

526
00:37:52,670 --> 00:37:56,539
嗯, 真是个大块头.
( Osha giggles ) Well, there's a big man.

527
00:37:56,572 --> 00:37:59,742
我敢说他有巨人的血统.
He has giants' blood in him or I'm the Queen.

528
00:37:59,775 --> 00:38:02,143
回去找你的衣服, 阿多.
Go back and find your clothes, Hodor.

529
00:38:02,177 --> 00:38:04,012
<i>去穿衣服吧.
- ( Laughs ) - Go dress.</i>

530
00:38:04,047 --> 00:38:05,579
阿多.
Hodor.

531
00:38:08,717 --> 00:38:10,918
长城之外真的有巨人吗?
Are there really giants beyond the Wall?

532
00:38:12,288 --> 00:38:15,257
有巨人, 还有比巨人更可怕的生物.
Giants and worse than giants.

533
00:38:15,291 --> 00:38:18,260
我跟你哥哥说过,
I tried telling your brother,

534
00:38:18,293 --> 00:38:20,094
他走错方向了.
he's marching the wrong way.

535
00:38:20,128 --> 00:38:23,632
所有的人马, 他们应该去北方, 孩子.
All these swords, they should be going North, boy.

536
00:38:23,666 --> 00:38:25,833
北方, 不是南方!
North, not south!

537
00:38:28,572 --> 00:38:30,972
寒风已然吹起.
The cold winds are rising.

538
00:38:31,007 --> 00:38:32,507
<i>( Leaves rustling )</i>

539
00:38:46,958 --> 00:38:49,293
他们被异鬼做了手脚.
They were touched by White Walkers.

540
00:38:50,829 --> 00:38:52,797
所以他们才会回来.
That's why they came back.

541
00:38:52,831 --> 00:38:55,699
所以他们的眼睛才会变成蓝色.
That's why their eyes turned blue.

542
00:38:55,733 --> 00:38:58,869
只有火能阻止他们.
Only fire will stop them.

543
00:39:00,806 --> 00:39:02,572
你怎么知道的?
How do you know that?

544
00:39:02,608 --> 00:39:04,342
我从书上看到的...
I read about it in a book--

545
00:39:04,376 --> 00:39:07,445
伊蒙师傅的图书馆里的一本非常古老的书.
a very old book in Maester Aemon's library.

546
00:39:09,981 --> 00:39:12,115
那本书还说了些什么?
What else did the book say?

547
00:39:12,150 --> 00:39:14,050
异鬼
The White Walkers

548
00:39:14,085 --> 00:39:16,853
在冰层之下沉睡了数千年.
sleep beneath the ice for thousands of years.

549
00:39:16,887 --> 00:39:19,423
当他们苏醒的时候...
And when they wake up--

550
00:39:20,425 --> 00:39:24,262
当他们苏醒的时候会怎样?
And when they wake up, what?

551
00:39:27,231 --> 00:39:29,733
我希望长城足够高.
I hope The Wall is high enough.

552
00:39:52,657 --> 00:39:54,757
( Men chattering )

553
00:40:02,264 --> 00:40:04,565
是夏雪, 夫人.
Summer snows, My Lady.

554
00:40:04,601 --> 00:40:07,635
罗柏马带来了北境的人马.
Robb's brought the North with him.

555
00:40:13,844 --> 00:40:15,710
河间地的领主们正在败退
The River Lords are falling back

556
00:40:15,746 --> 00:40:17,579
詹姆兰尼斯特在后面穷追不舍.
with Jaime Lannister at their heels.

557
00:40:17,614 --> 00:40:21,016
而泰温大人正带着另一支兰尼斯特军队从南方进逼.
And Lord Tywin is bringing around a second Lannister army from the South.

558
00:40:21,052 --> 00:40:23,820
我们的斥候报告说其规模比弑君者的更庞大.
Our scouts confirm it's even larger than the Kingslayer's.

559
00:40:23,855 --> 00:40:27,125
管他一支还是两支军队, 北境之王...
One army or two, the Kings in the North

560
00:40:27,159 --> 00:40:30,961
能够打垮十倍优势的敌人.
threw back hosts 10 times as large.

561
00:40:34,465 --> 00:40:36,132
母亲!
Mother!

562
00:40:39,538 --> 00:40:41,771
你气色很好.
You look well.

563
00:40:43,273 --> 00:40:47,043
凯特琳夫人, 在此动乱时刻见到您真是高兴.
Lady Catelyn, you're a welcome sight in these troubled times.

564
00:40:47,077 --> 00:40:49,545
我们没想到会在这里见到您, 夫人.
We had not thought to meet you here, My Lady.

565
00:40:50,514 --> 00:40:53,083
我也没想到会来这里.
I had not thought to be here.

566
00:40:53,117 --> 00:40:55,184
我想单独和我儿子讲几句话.
I would speak with my son alone.

567
00:40:55,219 --> 00:40:57,521
相信诸位大人能够理解.
I know you will forgive me, My Lords.

568
00:40:57,556 --> 00:40:59,789
你们听见夫人说的话了! 快动身!
You heard her! Move your asses!

569
00:40:59,824 --> 00:41:02,159
快点, 到外面去.
Come on, out.

570
00:41:02,195 --> 00:41:04,829
你也是, 葛雷乔伊. 你他妈的耳聋了吗?
You too, Greyjoy. Are you bloody deaf?

571
00:41:04,864 --> 00:41:06,766
不要担心, 夫人.
Have no fear, My Lady.

572
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:09,568
<i>我们会拿剑拥穿泰温兰尼斯特的屁眼...
We'll shove our swords up Tywin Lannister's bunghole</i>

573
00:41:09,601 --> 00:41:12,371
然后打下红堡救出奈德.
and then it's on to the Red Keep to free Ned.

574
00:41:12,405 --> 00:41:15,338
- 你这老鬼头, 罗德利克. - 大琼恩.
- You old devil, Rodrik. - Jon.

575
00:41:15,373 --> 00:41:17,708
你的功夫还没荒废, 是吗?
You're not wasting away, are you?

576
00:41:28,952 --> 00:41:31,788
我还清楚地记得你出生那天的样子...
I remember the day you came into this world

577
00:41:31,822 --> 00:41:34,858
脸红红的, 大声哭闹.
red-faced and squalling.

578
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:39,028
现在我却看到你率领着一支大军上战场.
And now I find you leading a host to war.

579
00:41:40,063 --> 00:41:42,465
- 没别人了. - 没别人?
- There was no one else. - No one?

580
00:41:42,500 --> 00:41:45,235
我刚才见到的那些人是谁?
Who were those men I saw here?

581
00:41:45,269 --> 00:41:48,338
- 他们都不是史塔克. - 他们都身经百战.
- None of them are Starks. - All of them are seasoned in battle.

582
00:41:48,373 --> 00:41:51,409
如果你想把我送回临冬城...
If you think you can send me back to Winterfell--

583
00:41:51,443 --> 00:41:53,710
哦, 我真希望能这么做.
Oh, would that I could.

584
00:41:56,782 --> 00:41:58,750
我收到了...
There was...

585
00:41:58,784 --> 00:42:01,219
一封信.
a letter.

586
00:42:03,655 --> 00:42:05,090
珊莎写来的.
From Sansa.

587
00:42:06,059 --> 00:42:08,360
你的意思是王后写来的.
From the Queen, you mean.

588
00:42:16,333 --> 00:42:19,436
- 上面没有提到艾莉亚. - 确实没有.
- There's no mention of Arya. - No.

589
00:42:30,047 --> 00:42:32,380
你带来多少人?
How many men do you have?

590
00:42:32,414 --> 00:42:34,817
一万八千.
18,000.

591
00:42:34,851 --> 00:42:37,318
如果我去君临向乔佛里屈膝下跪...
If I go to King's Landing and bend my knee to Joffrey--

592
00:42:37,353 --> 00:42:40,422
不, 那样你将永远无法离开.
you would never be allowed to leave. No.

593
00:42:40,456 --> 00:42:43,224
我们最大的希望... 或者说惟一的希望...
Our best hope-- our only hope--

594
00:42:43,259 --> 00:42:46,561
便是你能在战场上击败对手.
is that you can defeat them in the field.

595
00:42:46,596 --> 00:42:48,630
如果我战败?
And if I lose?

596
00:42:48,664 --> 00:42:51,199
你知道坦格利安家孩子们的下场吗...
Do you know what happened to the Targaryen children

597
00:42:51,233 --> 00:42:54,237
- 当君临城陷的时候? - 他们在睡梦中被屠杀.
- when the Mad King fell? - They were butchered in their sleep.

598
00:42:54,271 --> 00:42:56,972
是泰温兰尼斯特下的命令.
On the orders of Tywin Lannister.

599
00:42:57,007 --> 00:42:59,710
多年的时光并没有使他变仁慈一点.
And the years have not made him kinder.

600
00:43:02,813 --> 00:43:04,983
如果你战败,
If you lose,

601
00:43:05,016 --> 00:43:07,719
你的父亲会死,
your father dies,

602
00:43:07,753 --> 00:43:09,286
你的妹妹们也会死,
your sisters die,

603
00:43:09,320 --> 00:43:11,554
<i>我们都会死.
we die.</i>

604
00:43:14,125 --> 00:43:16,159
好吧, 那事情就简单了.
Well, that makes it simple then.

605
00:43:17,494 --> 00:43:19,494
我想是这样.
I suppose it does.

606
00:43:42,516 --> 00:43:45,751
现在最好由波隆和我两个过去.
From here it might be best if Bronn and I continue alone.

607
00:43:45,786 --> 00:43:48,356
对泰温之子提利昂来说最好.
Best for Tyrion son of Tywin.

608
00:43:48,389 --> 00:43:50,391
对我们来说可不好.
Not best for me.

609
00:43:50,425 --> 00:43:53,594
如果半人背叛我们,
If the half man betrays us,

610
00:43:53,628 --> 00:43:57,065
多夫之子夏嘎就会剁掉他的命根子...
Shagga Son of Dolf will cut off his manhood--

611
00:43:57,099 --> 00:43:59,635
拿去喂山羊, 我知道.
and feed it to the goats, yes.

612
00:44:02,139 --> 00:44:04,706
那好吧.
All right then.

613
00:44:04,740 --> 00:44:06,943
我要去见我父亲了.
Time to meet my father.

614
00:44:39,275 --> 00:44:42,077
- 提利昂. - 叔叔.
- Tyrion. - Uncle.

615
00:44:42,112 --> 00:44:43,980
父亲.
Father.

616
00:44:45,483 --> 00:44:48,483
看来关于你已死的传言不攻自破了.
The rumors of your demise were unfounded.

617
00:44:48,518 --> 00:44:51,920
真抱歉让您失望了.
Sorry to disappoint you.

618
00:44:51,954 --> 00:44:54,489
这些是什么人...
And who are these...

619
00:44:54,523 --> 00:44:56,757
<i>你的同伴?
Companions of yours?</i>

620
00:44:58,827 --> 00:45:01,260
这位是多夫之子夏嘎,
This is Shagga Son of Dolf,

621
00:45:01,295 --> 00:45:03,664
<i>石鸦部的酋长.
Chieftain of the Stone Crows.</i>

622
00:45:03,697 --> 00:45:08,068
<i>提魅之子提魅, 灼人部的首领.
Timett Son of Timett, ruler of the Burned Men.</i>

623
00:45:08,101 --> 00:45:12,840
<i>这位美少女是齐克之女齐拉
This fair maid is Chella daughter of Cheyk,</i>

624
00:45:12,873 --> 00:45:15,242
<i>黑耳部的领袖.
leader of the Black Ears.</i>

625
00:45:15,277 --> 00:45:18,646
而这位是波隆, 谁人之子来着...
And here we have Bronn son of...

626
00:45:18,681 --> 00:45:21,282
你不会认识他的.
You wouldn't know him.

627
00:45:23,286 --> 00:45:25,855
可否允许我为各位介绍我的父亲大人,
May I present My Lord Father,

628
00:45:25,889 --> 00:45:28,523
兰尼斯特家族的泰陀斯之子泰温,
Tywin son of Tytos of House Lannister,

629
00:45:28,559 --> 00:45:31,626
<i>凯岩城主暨西境守护.
Lord of Casterly Rock and Warden of the West?</i>

630
00:45:33,597 --> 00:45:36,233
非常感谢您为我出兵打仗.
Kind of you to go to war for me.

631
00:45:39,269 --> 00:45:41,204
你使我们别无选择.
You left us no choice.

632
00:45:41,239 --> 00:45:43,306
这事关家族的荣誉.
The honor of the House was at stake.

633
00:45:44,809 --> 00:45:47,978
你哥哥詹姆绝不会如此轻易地束手就擒的.
Your brother would never have submitted to capture so meekly.

634
00:45:48,012 --> 00:45:50,547
我们确实有所不同, 詹姆和我.
We have our differences, Jaime and I.

635
00:45:50,581 --> 00:45:52,750
他更勇敢. 而我更帅气.
He's braver. I'm better looking.

636
00:45:52,784 --> 00:45:55,119
他满身都是荣耀.
He's been covering himself in glory.

637
00:45:55,153 --> 00:45:58,389
詹姆在金牙城外击溃了三河诸侯,
Jaime smashed the River Lords at the Golden Tooth,

638
00:45:58,423 --> 00:46:02,092
现在正在围攻奔流城, 凯特琳史塔克的老家.
and now lays siege to Riverrun, Catelyn Stark's homeland.

639
00:46:02,126 --> 00:46:04,228
史塔克家在做什么? 艾德大人?
And the Starks? Lord Eddard?

640
00:46:04,262 --> 00:46:08,331
--现在是我们的人质. 他在地牢里无法带兵打仗.
--Is our hostage. He will lead no armies from his dungeon cell.

641
00:46:08,367 --> 00:46:10,400
我那美丽的姐姐是怎么说服国王
How did my sweet sister persuade the King

642
00:46:10,434 --> 00:46:12,302
囚禁他亲爱的朋友奈德的?
to imprison his dear friend Ned?

643
00:46:12,338 --> 00:46:16,307
劳勃拜拉席恩死了. 如今是乔佛里在君临执政.
Robert Baratheon is dead. Joffrey rules in King's Landing.

644
00:46:19,313 --> 00:46:21,280
你的意思是说是我姐姐在执政.
My sister rules, you mean.

645
00:46:22,483 --> 00:46:24,784
史塔克的儿子已经下令召集封臣.
Stark's son has called his banners.

646
00:46:24,818 --> 00:46:28,255
- 他正带着一支大军南下. - 不过是个毛头小子.
- He moves south with a strong host. - A green boy.

647
00:46:28,289 --> 00:46:30,056
等他尝到战斗的滋味就会...
One taste of battle and he'll run

648
00:46:30,090 --> 00:46:32,659
夹着尾巴逃回临冬城.
back to Winterfell wi his tail between his legs.

649
00:46:33,862 --> 00:46:35,362
也许吧.
Maybe.

650
00:46:35,396 --> 00:46:37,965
不过那小子确实很好战.
Though the boy does have a certain belligerence.

651
00:46:37,998 --> 00:46:40,501
你会喜欢他的.
You'd like him.

652
00:46:40,534 --> 00:46:44,572
既然我们说到打仗的事情,
While we're on the subject of war,

653
00:46:44,606 --> 00:46:47,307
我对这几位朋友做过承诺
I made promises to my friends here

654
00:46:47,342 --> 00:46:49,710
而兰尼斯特有债必还.
and a Lannister always pays his debts.

655
00:46:49,744 --> 00:46:52,813
<i>我们需要三千个头盔和盾牌,
We shall require 3,000 helms and shields,</i>

656
00:46:52,847 --> 00:46:55,081
还有刀剑, 长枪,
plus swords, pikes,

657
00:46:55,115 --> 00:46:56,916
护甲, 钉锤...
gorgets, maces--

658
00:46:56,951 --> 00:46:59,518
如果大人同意,
if it please My Lord,

659
00:46:59,552 --> 00:47:01,621
亚当爵士要我来报告, 北境军队
Ser Addam bids me report that the Northmen

660
00:47:01,655 --> 00:47:03,054
已经越过了颈泽.
have crossed the neck.

661
00:47:05,057 --> 00:47:07,525
小狼就要钻进狮口了.
The wolf rushes into the lion's jaws.

662
00:47:07,559 --> 00:47:11,797
好吧. 凯冯, 立刻下令敲鼓集合.
So be it. Kevan, command the drummers beat assembly.

663
00:47:13,300 --> 00:47:16,436
并送信给詹姆说我将前去同罗柏史塔克决战.
And send word to Jaime that I am moving against Robb Stark.

664
00:47:16,469 --> 00:47:18,438
遵命, 大人.
At once, My Lord.

665
00:47:31,387 --> 00:47:34,355
听说山地部落的人都是伟大的战士.
It is said that the men of the Mountain clans are great warriors.

666
00:47:34,389 --> 00:47:36,123
与我一同出兵作战
Ride with me against my enemies

667
00:47:36,157 --> 00:47:39,193
你们将得到我儿子承诺的一切, 甚至更多.
and you shall have all my son promised you and more.

668
00:47:39,228 --> 00:47:41,463
但这个半人得跟我们一起作战.
Only if the half man fights with us.

669
00:47:41,498 --> 00:47:44,934
直到我们拿到他答应的武器,
Until we hold the steel he pledged us,

670
00:47:44,969 --> 00:47:47,369
这小狮子的命是我们的.
the little lion's life is ours.

671
00:47:52,943 --> 00:47:55,612
<i>斥候报告说泰温大人正在北上.
Rodrik: The scouts report Lord Tywin moves north.</i>

672
00:47:55,646 --> 00:47:57,480
我们需要凭借险要地形截住他,
We need to get him on broken ground,

673
00:47:57,514 --> 00:47:59,181
使他的骑士无法发挥力量.
put his Knights at a disadvantage.

674
00:47:59,215 --> 00:48:01,318
不, 我们要从他侧面绕过去
No, we need to get around him

675
00:48:01,351 --> 00:48:04,253
并打破詹姆兰尼斯特对奔流城的围攻.
and break Jaime Lannister's siege of Riverrun.

676
00:48:04,289 --> 00:48:07,123
这样三河诸候就会加入我们的队伍.
Do that and the River Lords will join us.

677
00:48:07,157 --> 00:48:09,025
无论怎样做我们都需要先过绿叉河
To do either we need to cross the river

678
00:48:09,059 --> 00:48:10,726
而孪河城是过河的惟一路线.
and the only crossing is at The Twins.

679
00:48:10,760 --> 00:48:12,795
<i>佛雷大人控制着孪河桥.
Theon: Lord Frey controls that bridge.</i>

680
00:48:12,829 --> 00:48:14,396
他是你父亲的封臣.
Your father's bannerman.

681
00:48:14,431 --> 00:48:17,666
我父亲称他为 "迟到的佛雷大人"
"The late Lord Frey" my father calls him.

682
00:48:17,701 --> 00:48:21,204
当年三叉戟河之战, 他在战斗结束后才现身.
At the Trident, he didn't appear until the battle was done.

683
00:48:21,237 --> 00:48:25,275
不是每个人都把自己的誓言当回事的.
Some men takes their oaths more seriously than others.

684
00:48:27,244 --> 00:48:29,778
( Grunting )

685
00:48:32,682 --> 00:48:35,418
罗柏说得对. 我们需要那座桥.
Robb's right. We need that bridge.

686
00:48:35,452 --> 00:48:37,552
那么该怎么办?
So what's it going to be?

687
00:48:37,588 --> 00:48:40,989
我们先对付詹姆还是泰温?
Do we move against Jaime or Lord Tywin?

688
00:48:45,161 --> 00:48:46,695
打扰了, 大人.
Your pardon, my lords.

689
00:48:46,730 --> 00:48:49,398
<i>我们抓住了一个兰尼斯特军的斥候.
We've captured a Lannister scout.</i>

690
00:48:51,302 --> 00:48:54,637
别担心, 小伙子. 他不会活着离开这个帐篷.
Don't worry, lad. He won't b  leaving this tent with his head.

691
00:48:55,974 --> 00:48:57,641
你们在哪儿发现他的?
Where did you find him?

692
00:48:57,675 --> 00:48:59,809
在营地周围的树丛里.
In the brush above the encampment.

693
00:48:59,844 --> 00:49:01,711
<i>他好象正在估算人数.
He looked to be counting.</i>

694
00:49:12,157 --> 00:49:13,958
你算出来有多少人?
How high did you get?

695
00:49:16,327 --> 00:49:18,329
两万. 或许更多.
20,000. Maybe more.

696
00:49:19,364 --> 00:49:21,097
你不必自己动手行刑.
You don't have to do this yourself.

697
00:49:21,132 --> 00:49:22,699
您父亲会理解的...
Your father would understand--

698
00:49:22,733 --> 00:49:26,769
我父亲懂得仁慈, 如果不是非杀不可.
My father unrstands mercy, when there is room for it.

699
00:49:28,172 --> 00:49:30,005
他也懂得荣誉...
And he understands honor...

700
00:49:32,811 --> 00:49:35,077
和勇气.
and courage.

701
00:49:36,981 --> 00:49:38,815
放他走吧.
Let him go.

702
00:49:39,784 --> 00:49:42,184
罗柏.
Robb.

703
00:49:54,197 --> 00:49:57,164
去告诉泰温大人, 凛冬将至.
( Softly ) Tell Lord Tywin Winter is coming for him.

704
00:49:57,199 --> 00:50:02,135
两万北境大军正在南下, 看看他是不是真的能拉金屎.
20,000 Northerners marching south to find out if he really does shit gold.

705
00:50:04,206 --> 00:50:05,706
遵命, 大人.
Yes, My Lord.

706
00:50:05,739 --> 00:50:07,541
多谢, 大人.
Thank you, My Lord.

707
00:50:16,985 --> 00:50:20,688
你疯了吗, 孩子?! 放他走?
Are you touched, boy?! Letting him go?

708
00:50:20,722 --> 00:50:22,757
你又称我孩子了.
You call me boy again.

709
00:50:24,260 --> 00:50:25,893
下去吧.
Go on.

710
00:50:35,070 --> 00:50:36,302
( Growls )

711
00:50:42,909 --> 00:50:46,112
喂.
Oi.

712
00:50:51,184 --> 00:50:53,853
<i>国王陛下决定...
Pycelle: It is also the wish of His Grace</i>

713
00:50:53,887 --> 00:50:59,193
<i>尽忠职守的杰诺斯史林特,
that his loyal servant Janos Slynt,</i>

714
00:50:59,226 --> 00:51:02,329
<i>- 都城守卫队司令... - 艾伦爵士.
- Commander of the City Watch... - Ser Aron.</i>

715
00:51:02,364 --> 00:51:05,934
<i>立刻擢升为贵族...
...Be at once raised to the rank of Lord...</i>

716
00:51:05,967 --> 00:51:11,438
<i>- 盖尔斯大人. - ...赐予古老的赫伦堡,
- Lord Gyles. - ...And granted the ancient seat of Harrenhal,</i>

717
00:51:11,472 --> 00:51:15,309
<i>其子嗣将世代继承此等荣耀
and that his sons and grandsons shall hold this honor</i>

718
00:51:15,342 --> 00:51:20,447
<i>直到世界末日.
after him until the end of time.</i>

719
00:51:20,481 --> 00:51:22,981
( Lords mutter )

720
00:51:24,284 --> 00:51:27,619
为取代叛徒艾德史塔克,
In the place of the traitor Eddard Stark,

721
00:51:27,653 --> 00:51:32,324
<i>国王陛下决定由泰温兰尼斯特,
it is the wish of his Grace that Tywin Lannister,</i>

722
00:51:32,358 --> 00:51:36,161
<i>凯岩城主暨西境守护,
Lord of Casterly Rock and Warden of the West,</i>

723
00:51:36,195 --> 00:51:40,298
<i>担任国王之手.
be appointed Hand of the King.</i>

724
00:51:40,333 --> 00:51:42,233
最后,
Lastly,

725
00:51:42,268 --> 00:51:45,103
于此密谋四起, 动乱不堪之际,
in these times of treason and turmoil,

726
00:51:45,137 --> 00:51:48,373
<i>御前会议认为...
it is the view of the Council</i>

727
00:51:48,407 --> 00:51:53,644
乔佛里国王的生命安全
that the life and safety

728
00:51:50,976 --> 00:51:53,644
of King Joffrey

729
00:51:53,679 --> 00:51:57,916
实乃第一要务.
be of paramount importance.

730
00:51:59,518 --> 00:52:02,052
巴利斯坦赛尔弥爵士.
Ser Barristan Selmy.

731
00:52:08,393 --> 00:52:11,896
陛下, 我听候您的差遣.
Your Grace, I am yours to command.

732
00:52:11,931 --> 00:52:14,032
请起, 巴利斯坦爵士.
Rise, Ser Barristan.

733
00:52:14,902 --> 00:52:17,003
你可以卸下头盔了.
You may remove your helm.

734
00:52:21,943 --> 00:52:24,545
<i>长久以来你为国效命，尽忠职守.
You have served the Realm long and faithfully.</i>

735
00:52:24,579 --> 00:52:28,550
<i>七国上下每个人都对你心怀感激.
Every man and woman in the Seven Kingdoms owes you thanks.</i>

736
00:52:28,585 --> 00:52:31,853
然而是时候让你卸下你的铠甲和宝剑了.
But it is time to put aside your armor and your sword.

737
00:52:31,887 --> 00:52:34,789
<i>你该安享晚年, 并自豪地回顾...
It is time to rest and look back with pride</i>

738
00:52:34,824 --> 00:52:36,458
你长久以来的功绩了.
on your many years of service.

739
00:52:36,492 --> 00:52:38,626
<i>( Murmuring )</i>

740
00:52:38,661 --> 00:52:41,096
陛下, 御林铁卫乃是宣誓效命的兄弟.
Your Grace, the Kingsguard is a sworn brotherhood.

741
00:52:41,130 --> 00:52:43,297
<i>我们必须终身守誓.
Our vows are taken for life.</i>

742
00:52:43,333 --> 00:52:45,835
惟有一死才能解除我们的神圣使命.
Only death relieves us of our sacred trust.

743
00:52:45,869 --> 00:52:49,572
是谁的死, 巴利斯坦爵士? 是你还是你的国王?
Whose death, Ser Barristan? Yours or your King's?

744
00:52:49,606 --> 00:52:52,474
<i>我父亲的死就是你的责任.
Joffrey: You let my father die.</i>

745
00:52:52,509 --> 00:52:55,445
你太老了, 谁都保护不了.
You're too old to protect anybody.

746
00:52:57,748 --> 00:53:00,483
- 陛下-- - 御前会议已经决定
- Your Grace-- - The Council has determined

747
00:53:00,518 --> 00:53:02,952
由詹姆兰尼斯特爵士接替你的职务
that Ser Jaime Lannister will take your place

748
00:53:02,987 --> 00:53:05,255
<i>担任御林铁卫队长.
as Lord Commander of the Kingsguard.</i>

749
00:53:05,289 --> 00:53:06,824
那个人玷污了自己的宝剑
The man who profaned his blade

750
00:53:06,858 --> 00:53:09,059
杀死了他宣誓要保护的国王!
with the blood of the King he had sworn to defend!

751
00:53:09,094 --> 00:53:11,027
小心一点, 爵士.
Careful, Ser.

752
00:53:11,061 --> 00:53:12,762
我们并非不知感恩
We have nothing but gratitude

753
00:53:12,797 --> 00:53:15,266
您的长期贡献有目共睹, 爵士.
for your long service, good Ser.

754
00:53:15,300 --> 00:53:17,768
您将得到一座坚固的海滨城堡,
You shall be given a stout Keep beside the sea,

755
00:53:17,802 --> 00:53:20,137
以及满足您需要的大批仆役.
with servants to look after your every need.

756
00:53:20,170 --> 00:53:22,371
给我一个养老的地方
A hall to die in

757
00:53:22,407 --> 00:53:24,807
<i>以及为我送终的人.
and men to bury me.</i>

758
00:53:26,409 --> 00:53:29,445
我既生为一名骑士.
I am a Knight.

759
00:53:29,480 --> 00:53:32,516
也要死得像个骑士.
I shall die a Knight.

760
00:53:38,456 --> 00:53:40,590
像个没穿衣服的骑士, 是吧.
A naked Knight, apparently.

761
00:53:40,625 --> 00:53:42,760
( Laughter )

762
00:53:51,735 --> 00:53:55,172
即便现在我仍可以像切蛋糕一样把你们五个通通砍倒!
Even now I could cut through the five of you like carving a cake!

763
00:53:59,344 --> 00:54:01,878
拿去, 小子!
Here, boy!

764
00:54:01,913 --> 00:54:04,347
把它熔了加到铁王座上吧.
Melt it down and add it to the others.

765
00:54:18,862 --> 00:54:20,829
<i>( Doors creak, clang )</i>

766
00:54:20,864 --> 00:54:23,199
如果在场各位还有其他事...
If any man in this hall has other matters

767
00:54:23,233 --> 00:54:26,367
请现在向国王陛下禀报
to set before His Grace, let him speak now

768
00:54:26,402 --> 00:54:29,639
否则退朝.
or go forth and hold his silence.

769
00:54:32,309 --> 00:54:34,445
陛下.
Your Grace.

770
00:54:34,478 --> 00:54:36,847
请上前来, 小姐.
Come forward, My Lady.

771
00:54:38,617 --> 00:54:41,353
<i>史塔克家族的珊莎小姐.
Steward: The Lady Sansa of House Stark.</i>

772
00:54:42,889 --> 00:54:46,291
珊莎, 你有事禀报国王陛下和御前会议?
Do you have some business for the King and the Council, Sansa?

773
00:54:46,326 --> 00:54:48,159
是的.
I do.

774
00:54:53,032 --> 00:54:56,134
启禀陛下, 我要为我父亲请求您的慈悲,
As it please Your Grace, I ask mercy for my father,

775
00:54:56,168 --> 00:54:59,637
艾德史塔克大人, 前任国王之手.
Lord Eddard Stark, who was Hand of the King.

776
00:54:59,672 --> 00:55:02,539
叛国大罪好似带毒的野草.
Treason is a noxious weed.

777
00:55:02,574 --> 00:55:06,744
- 必须连根拔除... - 让她说下去.
- It should be torn out, root-- - Let her speak.

778
00:55:06,780 --> 00:55:09,481
我要听听她的话.
I want to hear what she says.

779
00:55:09,516 --> 00:55:11,650
感谢您, 陛下.
Thank you, Your Grace.

780
00:55:11,684 --> 00:55:14,288
你要否认你父亲所犯罪行?
Do you deny your father's crime?

781
00:55:14,322 --> 00:55:18,793
不, 诸位大人. 我明白他必须接受惩罚.
No, My Lords. I know he must be punished.

782
00:55:18,827 --> 00:55:20,827
我请求的只是慈悲为怀.
All I ask is mercy.

783
00:55:20,862 --> 00:55:23,731
<i>我知道我父亲必定对其所为懊悔不已.
I know My Lord father must regret what he did.</i>

784
00:55:23,766 --> 00:55:26,068
他是劳勃国王的好友, 他敬爱国王.
He was King Robert's friend and he loved him.

785
00:55:26,101 --> 00:55:28,302
你们知道他是真心敬爱他.
You all know he loved him.

786
00:55:28,338 --> 00:55:31,940
他从未想当国王之手, 直到国王要求他.
He never wanted to be Hand until the King asked him.

787
00:55:31,974 --> 00:55:35,376
他必定是受人蛊惑... 蓝礼大人或史坦尼斯大人
They must have lied to him-- Lord Renly or Lord Stannis

788
00:55:35,409 --> 00:55:38,211
或是其他什么人. 他们欺骗了他!
or somebody. They must have lied!

789
00:55:38,246 --> 00:55:40,715
他说我不是国王.
He said I wasn't the King.

790
00:55:40,748 --> 00:55:42,815
他为什么要那样说?
Why did he say that?

791
00:55:42,851 --> 00:55:45,119
他受了重伤.
He was badly hurt.

792
00:55:45,152 --> 00:55:48,021
派席尔大学士给他服用了罂粟花奶.
Maester Pycelle was giving him milk of the poppy.

793
00:55:48,054 --> 00:55:52,224
当时他神智不清. 否则他绝不会那样说的.
He wasn't himself. Otherwise h  never would have said it.

794
00:55:54,561 --> 00:55:58,431
孩子对父亲的信赖... 多么单纯天真.
A child's faith... Such sweet innocence.

795
00:55:58,465 --> 00:56:02,135
<i>可是人们不是常说, 智慧之言往往来自
And yet they say wisdom oft comes</i>

796
00:56:02,170 --> 00:56:04,003
孩童之口么.
from the mouths of babes.

797
00:56:04,038 --> 00:56:08,175
但叛国就是叛国!
Treason is treason!

798
00:56:11,313 --> 00:56:13,480
你还有什么事?
Anything else?

799
00:56:15,050 --> 00:56:18,452
如果您心里仍然有我,
If you still have any affection in your heart for me,

800
00:56:18,485 --> 00:56:21,987
请成全我这个心愿吧, 陛下.
please do me this kindness, Your Grace.

801
00:56:31,565 --> 00:56:33,831
你的肺腑之言感动了我.
Your sweet words have moved me.

802
00:56:36,235 --> 00:56:38,802
但你父亲必须先俯首认罪.
But your father has to confess.

803
00:56:38,838 --> 00:56:42,440
他必须承认我是他的国王...
He has to confess and say that I'm the King...

804
00:56:45,342 --> 00:56:47,478
不然我无法手下留情.
Or there'll be no mercy for him.

805
00:56:51,949 --> 00:56:54,050
他一定会的.
He will.

806
00:57:00,925 --> 00:57:04,061
<i>( Music playing )</i>

807
